{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496430/extras/Shadowcity_Case_Files_Steam_Page_Banners.png?t=1739347772\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496430/extras/Shadowcity_Case_Files_Steam_Page_Banners2.png?t=1739347772\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You weren\u2019t always the most feared criminal in Shadow City. Experience the gritty tale of how you clawed your way to power. Forge alliances or crush your rivals, where every choice determines who survives, who falls, and who remains by your side in Shadow City.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496430/extras/Shadowcity_Case_Files_Steam_Page_Banners3.png?t=1739347772\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Negotiate with Shadow City\u2019s elite: bribe, threaten, or charm them into following your lead. Every relationship matters, and every favor comes with a price.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496430/extras/Shadowcity_Case_Files_Steam_Page_Banners4.png?t=1739347772\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every decision, whether in loyalty or betrayal, shapes your rise to power. Choose how you seize control: through fear, cunning deals, or something more brutal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496430/extras/Shadowcity_Case_Files_Steam_Page_Banners5.png?t=1739347772\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A single mistake can topple even the mightiest king. From personal vendettas to citywide fallout, your choices echo far beyond the throne.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496430/extras/Shadowcity_Case_Files_Steam_Page_Banners6.png?t=1739347772\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your actions set the stage for each chapter and ultimately influence the events of <i><strong>Shadow City Mysteries: A Clockwork Noir</strong></i>. The fate of Shadow City rests in your hands.</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3496430?t=1739347772","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496430/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1739347772","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496430/c8a30da59c301469d689fc63d7bccaade8945e4b/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739347772","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496430/c8a30da59c301469d689fc63d7bccaade8945e4b/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739347772","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[5],"notes":"The developers describe the content like this:\r\n\r\nWith a dark noir setting the game potentially has violence, sex, drugs, and other mature topics alluded to or on screen."},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3496430/extras/Shadowcity_Case_Files_Steam_Page_Banners.png?t=1739347772\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/s